summary: This document is a chain of emails from June 2019 arranging a conference call to discuss victim interviews in the Epstein case. It involves FBI personnel and a child forensic interviewer coordinating logistics for a call scheduled for June 28, 2019.

events.title: Epstein victim interviews conference call
events.description: A scheduled unclassified conference call to discuss victim interviews in the Epstein case, set for 2 pm Eastern Time.

keyFacts: A conference call was scheduled for June 28, 2019, at 2 pm Eastern Time to discuss victim interviews in the Epstein case.
The call was organized by the FBI NY Criminal Division Violent Crimes Task Force and involved a Child/Adolescent Forensic Interviewer.
The email chain shows coordination between FBI personnel and forensic interviewers regarding the logistics of the victim interview discussions.
